    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>While the duck is in the oven, wash, then cut your <strong>pak choi</strong> in half, separating the <strong>white base</strong> and <strong>green tops</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add your <strong>hoisin sauce </strong>to a small bowl with a tiny splash of<strong> cold water </strong>to loosen it</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
