    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>udon noodles</strong> to a large bowl, cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Set aside to soak for 4-5 min</p><p>Tip: Gently separate the noodles with a fork!</p><p>Drain the <strong>soaked noodles</strong></p><p>When the duck has 7 min left, add the <strong>sliced spring greens</strong> to the oven for 6-7 min or until crispy – this is your <strong>crispy 'seaweed'</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
