        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat the reserved large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat with the <strong>reserved duck fat & duck jelly</strong></p><p>Once melted, add your<strong> ginger & garlic paste </strong>and <strong>soy sauce </strong>with<strong> </strong>a pinch of<strong> sugar </strong>and cook for 1-2 min, then add the <strong>pak choi</strong> <strong>white base</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p>",
